      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in sun-exposed areas. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up to address some minor rattles. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
