      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic driving experience with this reliable and well-maintained vehicle! It's in good condition overall, showing some minor signs of previous use that don't detract from its great performance. This car has been cared for and is ready to hit the road with its next owner today!",
